  "description": "This dataset contains MEG recordings acquired during a cued recall task designed to investigate sustained neural representations of personally familiar people and places. Participants were cued to recall specific individuals and locations while brain activity was monitored, enabling investigation of how the brain maintains and represents autobiographical memories and social knowledge.",
